platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Terry Cavanagh’s Super Hexagon is quite simply one of the most challenging games we’ve ever played. A pulsating chiptunes soundtrack underscores the danger as swirling walls close in around you and you race to escape the contracting maze. With the geometric action heaping on the punishment (the easiest difficulty is appropriately labeled “Hard”), every small achievement feels like a massive victory, whether you’re topping your high score or overcoming a singularly tricky section.

Terry Cavanagh’s Super Hexagon is quite simply one of the most challenging games we’ve ever played. A pulsating chiptunes soundtrack underscores the danger as swirling walls close in around you and you race to escape the contracting maze. With the geometric action heaping on the punishment (the easiest difficulty is appropriately labelled “Hard”), every small achievement feels like a massive victory, whether you’re topping your high score or overcoming a singularly tricky section.

シンプルな操作ながら難易度が高く、思わず夢中になるおもしろさ - テリー・カバナーによる大人気ゲーム「Super Hexagon」。押し寄せる壁とチップチューンの相乗効果による緊迫感の中、集中力と反射神経を駆使して迷路空間を脱出しよう。一つ危機を乗り越えても、すぐに次の難関がやってくるハードさだからこそ（一番低い難易度でも「Hard」）、ハイスコアを叩き出したときはもちろん、小技をこなしたときでさえも、大きな達成感を味わえる。
獨立遊戲開發者 Terry Cavanagh 開發的《Super Hexagon》（超能六方體）簡單說就是一項超高難度的遊戲。旋轉色塊隨快節奏的電玩晶片音樂步步逼近，玩家必須設法逃脫不斷內縮的迷陣，著實倍感驚險緊張。在幾何圖形越堆越多的難關下（遊戲最基本難易程度即設定為「困難」），無論是刷高個人分數或者逃過特別麻煩的陣局，只要贏得一點小勝利，都會令你大快人心。

Conçu par Terry Cavanagh, Super Hexagon est sans aucun doute l’un des jeux les plus ardus auxquels nous ayons jamais joué. La bande son 8-bit palpitante ponctue le danger omniprésent, alors que les murs tournoyants d’un labyrinthe nous encerclent et nous pressent d’en trouver l’issue. Entre géométrie oppressante et difficulté impitoyable, chaque moment de succès procure la sensation d’une immense victoire, que vous amélioriez votre record ou que vous sortiez indemne d’une situation périlleuse.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: This is still one of our favorites. Few games are this satisfying to master.
